What's so stingy about me!?

9
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:41,800
Is Matsumoto really a stingy bastard?
The truth will be revealed tonight.

10
00:00:55,520 --> 00:01:00,560
The Too Stingy Ochoko-Matsumoto's Trial is now in open session.

11
00:01:00,990 --> 00:01:03,490
Prosecutor and plaintiff group, please enter the court.

12
00:01:24,010 --> 00:01:28,120
